Reasoning: The paper discusses the use of information retrieval and knowledge graphs to improve e-book platforms, which falls under the category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR). The addition of intelligence and machine learning to the platform also suggests the involvement of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) and Machine Learning (cs.LG). The focus on user experience and interaction with the platform suggests the involvement of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). Finally, the use of random walk for information retrieval suggests the involvement of Deep Learning (cs.DL).
